4 reasons to switch

All-in-One Multi-chain Wallet with Cross‑Chain Swaps

Manage Bitcoin, Cardano, Solana, Ethereum, EVMs, SVMs and Flow — all from a single wallet. Swap assets across chains without leaving the app.

Deep Hardware Wallet Support

Secure your crypto with Ledger (USB + Bluetooth), Trezor, Keystone, OneKey, GridPlus, and BitBox — more hardware options than most wallets.

Social Login for Instant Access

Create a wallet in seconds using Google, Facebook, Discord, or X (Twitter) — no seed phrase required. Non-custodial.
